      <t>This document proposes an extension to Seamless Bidirectional Forwarding Detection (S-BFD). The S-BFD initiator will send packets that carry extra information, and this enables reflector to act as a proxy, and respond with the extra information in consideration. This document updates RFC 7880.</t>
